dataset <- read.csv("5361.csv")
dataset2 <- read.csv("5361_8.25.csv")

4377 vs 5361

dataset3 <- dataset2[-c(1:20),]
Data4377 <- read.csv("4377.csv")
dataset3$RH2 <- Data4377$RH

ggplot(dataset3, aes(X.)) + geom_line(aes(y = RH2, color = "4377")) + geom_line(aes(y = RH, color = "5361")) + ylab("Humidity")+ xlab("Scale")

plot(dataset3$RH2, dataset3$RH, xlab = "4377", ylab = "5361")

lm(RH ~ RH2, dataset3)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = RH ~ RH2, data = dataset3)
## 
## Coefficients:
## (Intercept)          RH2  
##     -5.3950       0.9473
Data4377$RH2 <- (0.9473 * Data4377$RH) + 6.4224
plot(Data4377$RH2, dataset3$RH, xlab = "4377", ylab = "5361")

lm(dataset3$RH ~ Data4377$RH2)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = dataset3$RH ~ Data4377$RH2)
## 
## Coefficients:
##  (Intercept)  Data4377$RH2  
##       -11.82          1.00

5354 vs 5361

data5354 <- read.csv("5354.22.csv")
dataset <- read.csv("5361.22.csv")

colnames(dataset) <- c("X", "DateTime", "Temp", "RH")
colnames(data5354) <- c("X", "DateTime", "Temp", "RH")

joined <- inner_join(data5354, dataset, by = "DateTime")

ggplot(joined, aes(X.x)) + geom_line(aes(y = RH.x, color = "5354")) + geom_line(aes(y = RH.y, color = "5361")) + ylab("Humidity") + xlab("Scale")   

plot(joined$RH.y, joined$RH.x, xlab = "5361", ylab = "5354")

lm(RH.x ~ RH.y, joined)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = RH.x ~ RH.y, data = joined)
## 
## Coefficients:
## (Intercept)         RH.y  
##      0.2417       0.9764
joined$RH2 <- ( 0.9764  * joined$RH.y) + 0.2417       
plot(joined$RH.y, joined$RH2, xlab = "5361", ylab = "5361")

lm(joined$RH.x ~ joined$RH2)
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = joined$RH.x ~ joined$RH2)
## 
## Coefficients:
## (Intercept)   joined$RH2  
##   5.504e-05    1.000e+00
